room_title: Escape room "The Hacker's Lair" by Lock City Escape Games in Carrollton
room_description: You are part of a G.B.I team dispatched to Carrollton, Georgia in order to investigate the residence of a recently discovered hacker. Unfortunately, the hacker got away for the time being, but his computer is still at the site uploading a large scale virus meant to corrupt the internet. Race against the clock in order to save the internet!
